hear you say that some legislator, some

14:01.243 --> 14:18.853
self-appointed important Aggie called you up to 
get so-and-so passed or get so-and-so admitted,

14:01.243 --> 14:18.853
no outside information. If you were looking back 
on those... Next to nothing. I can't think of

