anything on that. Looking back over those years in 
the department, which department members do you

14:26.535 --> 14:36.293
think deserve the greatest praise? I'm not going 
to ask you the negative. If you were giving pats on

14:38.357 --> 14:43.407
the back, who would get the most?

14:52.837 --> 14:55.439
I think, in many ways, Gary Holder. Why? Explain. I 
don't disagree with you. I'm just asking you to

